{"blocks":[{"key":"2kfiv","text":"Mount sections on positively charged slides and bake overnight at 70° C. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"r48t","text":"Prepare primary antibody dilution kit (depending on antibody concentration) for Ventana Benchmark XT automatic staining platform (Roche Diagnostics, Indianapolis, IN) according to the manufacturer's protocol.
